# Task 13 – Access Control for Book Table

## Project

Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This task configures Access Control Lists (ACLs) for the Book table to implement role-based security.

## ACL Configuration

### Read
- Student
- Librarian

### Create
- Librarian

### Write
- Librarian

### Delete
- Librarian

## Testing

- Verified Student has read-only access.
- Verified Librarian has full CRUD access.
- Verified unauthorized users cannot modify book records.

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- Access Control Lists (ACL)
- Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

## Status

Completed
